Pokedex

Egg group - MONSTER / DRAGON

The eggs of this dragon are laid inside of glaciers. It must build tunnels through the ice to survive after birth.
Its backshell is formed from Totsicle's tough eggshell. The icicles on their heads are used to impale prey.
